  "elapsed_s": 6.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, it was just a little bit left over bricks so we started kind of to put up like this high up kind of, you know, because it was scattered, the things of the next day he tried to do.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the next day, they went-- came.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They-- all the men had to shave their beards down, my father too.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "He said there was no use of it to others.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And-- well, he was already a neighbor there, and they were talking and my father said, they say that [INAUDIBLE] everybody [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Something-- I don't know from-- he mentioned where something he-- place he saw.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- but--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The Hungarians.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, the Hungarians, but they were under the Nazi--",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Orders.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Orders, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, hundreds, hundreds of--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know, I don't know.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No, it was not maybe really a thousand or maybe--",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In the hundreds, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Maybe it was thousands.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I know hundreds, but, as I say, the first few days, you know, we had from home some stuff.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Once a day they gave us soup-- soup, you know, things.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So we had to stay in the line for it but then, you know, besides us, especially there were children, everybody tried, oh, I don't need it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, if a mother said, Regina, have a [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh no, I'm not hungry, no matter how because you were pushing it, stretching it because we didn't know what's what.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so-- but it was really terrible there, because the-- the sanitation started getting bad outside.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The-- the thing started raining, shoes in the mud, kind of sinking in, and the latrine, it was not prepared.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
